  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>原创 <span>AI沃茨</span> <span>2026-03-19 18:34</span> <span style=\"display: inline-block;\">意大利</span></p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=daaf0e91&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FVNz1x8bH8FwYicpLSFbD20FrhfR3ibSDiaWibAdF23oAV5Dwfehc0Sa7cxVziaFVasS36EPka8MWBIK3zEGTIU4ric9MvUz2C2gmDjvia9ymNTSaEI%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p>这下真的有手就会了</p>\n  <div data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);border-radius: 12px;line-height: 2em;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"color: rgb(143, 149, 158);letter-spacing: 0px;font-weight: 400;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);border-radius: 12px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <div data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"color: #8f959e;letter-spacing: 0px;font-weight: 400;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;margin: 0 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px 0px;border: 1px solid rgba(NaN, 10, NaN, 1);background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);border-radius: 12px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n     <h2 style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-weight: 400;font-family: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 16px;line-height: 2em;margin: 0px 0px 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;\">如果说有什么样格式的数据是我最近用OpenClaw会头疼的，</span></h2>\n     <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-weight: 400;font-family: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 16px;line-height: 2em;margin: 16px 0px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\">现阶段一定是视频，不管是视频剪辑，视频总结，视频生成，给视频加字幕都要消耗大量的Token。接入的Skills设定不够好的话，真不如我回到视频Agent们上做。</span></span></p>\n     <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n     <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-weight: 400;font-family: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 16px;line-height: 2em;margin: 16px 0px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\">视频生成这块更是拉完了，</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-weight: 400;font-family: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 16px;line-height: 2em;margin: 16px 0px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\">Clawhub上的配置大部份都是把视频模型的API封装成Skill，或者像是if else工作流一样，把脚本生成，图片生成，视频生成分别前后交给不同的模型完成，最后拼接在一起。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-weight: 400;font-family: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 16px;line-height: 2em;margin: 16px 0px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\">感觉一下子给我干回到视频Agent出现前的蛮荒时代了。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-weight: 400;font-family: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 16px;line-height: 2em;margin: 16px 0px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\">长话短说，前Vidu团队的成员出来做了一个新的视频Agent，叫Pexo。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-weight: 400;font-family: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 16px;line-height: 2em;margin: 16px 0px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\">这是一个你不需要懂怎么写提示词的Agent，只要跟它聊天，就能得到自己想要的视频，而且它现在就可以在OpenClaw里用了。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-weight: 400;font-family: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 16px;line-height: 2em;margin: 16px 0px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">所以，这次我跟Pexo一拍即合，挖到了5个OpenClaw做视频的使用场景，包括了产品广告，UGC视频，品牌宣传片，动漫短剧和音乐MV。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-weight: 400;font-family: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 16px;line-height: 2em;margin: 16px 0px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"飞书文档 - 图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100022022\" data-ratio=\"0.6018518518518519\" data-w=\"1080\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9cd3440e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FVNz1x8bH8Fy7aZcYs7vmoRvWaVFm0UoxDibClWKmjdKbGESbDOHhACDAg577AfurXPWHX8pghZmdq2kpSaLfh1nDAPyQsXvnC0Jfx5uWq0nk%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-weight: 400;font-family: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 16px;line-height: 2em;margin: 16px 0px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\">Pexo已经上线了ClawHub，所以安装过程非常简单。我直接在飞书的对话框里，把从ClawHub上下载的ZIP文件发给我的OpenClaw，它就自动完成了安装。然后，去Pexo的官网注册个账号，在设置里找到API Key，再把这个Key发给OpenClaw，整个配置就完成了。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-weight: 400;font-family: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 16px;line-height: 2em;margin: 16px 0px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\">这时候就可以把提示语发给OpenClaw干活了。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-weight: 400;font-family: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 16px;line-height: 2em;margin: 16px 0px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\">目前来说，单次可以生成最长</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" pingfang=\"\" helvetica=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\"><span leaf=\"\">两</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\">分钟</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\">的视频，支持的视频尺寸包括16:9，9:16和1:1，生成完成后，飞书会直接返给你一个视频的下载链接。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-weight: 400;font-family: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 16px;line-height: 2em;margin: 16px 0px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"飞书文档 - 图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100022023\" data-ratio=\"0.7490740740740741\" data-w=\"1080\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ceaaf2d5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FVNz1x8bH8FxfibluEB5DBIrSvxrAKcMuz31GFuOzqWot0h4H91INCjARYDIyxQCLKXowcMXGc25hsk3gVLjUdJaSiaoOWk1MJqRbhNPOxPq40%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-weight: 400;font-family: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 16px;line-height: 2em;margin: 16px 0px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\">甚至还可以输入多图片让Pexo生成一个tvc，比如说，我这里给了它一张人物图片和我随手拍的香水图片，我其实都没有给它很复杂的提示，就是非常简单的告诉它，做一支广告片，</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100022024\" data-ratio=\"0.6555555555555556\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9b82cfc3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FVNz1x8bH8FxX23Yf7cAjTNLEUtRemGF9gHxqvkJsUOsx6xG3moQaiaX63TCJX3az934jia6c8JZWK3rWEfprTt5vqQZbCcoARZEVSCyAKSnAs%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n     <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-weight: 400;font-family: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 16px;line-height: 2em;margin: 16px 0px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\">然后我们就能得到这样的一组视频，包括视频基调，分镜，音乐，镜头逻辑，这些它都是给我策划好了。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-weight: 400;font-family: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 16px;line-height: 2em;margin: 16px 0px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\">它能够识别出来我这款香水是壁炉火光的香型，然后根据壁炉火光这个主题做出相应的视觉元素，人物的动态也处理得非常自然，说明是接了有世界知识的模型的。</span></span></p>\n     <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n     <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-weight: 400;font-family: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 16px;line-height: 2em;margin: 16px 0px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果对这个视频不是很满意的话，除了可以在飞书里继续跟它对话修改，还可以直接回到Pexo的网页端，找到这次生成任务的完整记录，然后对视频进行更精细的调整。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-weight: 400;font-family: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 16px;line-height: 2em;margin: 16px 0px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"飞书文档 - 图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100022027\" data-ratio=\"0.5851851851851851\" data-w=\"1080\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=20f9f5f2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FVNz1x8bH8Fx0DFVdHo7wp3xo2DFZtjA5TCgFsf4LgdB006ah0yPknrQS6EBAgXDIWtjmiaCkHvsPc5k2zsZWg9nEqXj5DbO3GJZy28icVUSX0%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-weight: 400;font-family: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 16px;line-height: 2em;margin: 16px 0px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\">比如，我还是沿用上面的这个人物，同时给它配上一张精华液的图片，让他给我做出一个这个人物使用该精华液的 UGC 视频，Pexo 上同样支持上传图片、视频和音频进行辅助创作。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-weight: 400;font-family: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 16px;line-height: 2em;margin: 16px 0px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: &quot;PingFang S